    "Britto et al. (2016) only adopted these two dimensions in their extended GSE taxonomy study, because they argued that empirical evidence exists which supports their influence on the organizational level.",
    "This is important because projects are usually carried out at the organizational level.",
    "Similarly, Siakas (2002) found these two dimensions directly influencing organizational culture, and Siakas and Siakas (2016) only included these two dimensions in their Cultural and Organizational Diversity Evaluation (CODE) tool.",
    "We built on evidence from studies using Hofstede's framework and through our empirical differentiation from his conceptualization, we addressed our research questions.",
